title: Microdiplatys campodeiformis
text: Microdiplatys campodeiformis is an <a href="extinction">extinct</a> species of <a href="earwig">earwig</a> in the family <a href="Protodiplatyidae">Protodiplatyidae</a>. It is one of only two species in the genus Microdiplatys, the other being "<a href="Microdiplatys%20oculatus">Microdiplatys oculatus</a>".
